<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8"><meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Marketing & Automatización — 303 Creative Studio®</title>
<link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="/logo.png">
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Outfit:wght@200;300;400;500;600;700;800&family=Syne:wght@400;500;600;700;800&family=DM+Sans:ital,opsz,wght@0,9..40,200;0,9..40,300;0,9..40,400;0,9..40,500;0,9..40,600;1,9..40,300;1,9..40,400&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
:root{--black:#0a0a0a;--white:#fafafa;--gray-50:#f5f5f7;--gray-100:#e8e8ed;--gray-200:#d2d2d7;--gray-400:#86868b;--gray-600:#6e6e73;--accent:#c8a97e;--accent-light:#e4d5c1;--accent-dark:#a68b5e;--font-display:'Syne',sans-serif;--font-body:'DM Sans',sans-serif;--font-heading:'Outfit',sans-serif;--ease-out:cubic-bezier(.16,1,.3,1)}*,*::before,*::after{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box}html{scroll-behavior:smooth;font-size:16px;-webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased}body{font-family:var(--font-body);background:var(--white);color:var(--black);overflow-x:hidden;line-height:1.6}
.nav{position:fixed;top:0;left:0;right:0;z-index:1000;padding:0 48px;height:56px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;backdrop-filter:saturate(180%) blur(20px);background:rgba(250,250,250,.92);border-bottom:.5px solid rgba(0,0,0,.06)}.nav-logo{height:28px;opacity:.9}.nav-links{display:flex;gap:32px;list-style:none}.nav-links a{font-size:.78rem;font-weight:400;color:var(--gray-600);text-decoration:none;transition:color .3s}.nav-links a:hover{color:var(--black)}.nav-cta{font-size:.72rem;font-weight:500;padding:8px 20px;background:var(--black);color:var(--white);border:none;border-radius:14px;cursor:pointer;text-decoration:none;transition:all .3s var(--ease-out)}
.page-hero{padding:160px 24px 100px;text-align:center;background:linear-gradient(180deg,#0a0a0a,#0d0f18);position:relative;overflow:hidden}.page-hero .tag{font-size:.68rem;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:.25em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--accent);margin-bottom:16px}.page-hero h1{font-family:var(--font-heading);font-size:clamp(2.5rem,5vw,4rem);font-weight:700;color:var(--white);line-height:1.08;letter-spacing:-.03em;margin-bottom:20px}.page-hero p{font-size:1.05rem;font-weight:300;color:rgba(255,255,255,.45);max-width:560px;margin:0 auto;line-height:1.7}
section{padding:100px 24px}.inner{max-width:900px;margin:0 auto}.section-tag{font-size:.68rem;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:.25em;text-transform:uppercase;background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--accent-dark),var(--accent));-webkit-background-clip:text;-webkit-text-fill-color:transparent;margin-bottom:16px}h2{font-family:var(--font-heading);font-size:clamp(1.8rem,3.5vw,2.6rem);font-weight:700;line-height:1.1;letter-spacing:-.025em;margin-bottom:20px}.text-block{font-size:1rem;font-weight:300;color:var(--gray-600);line-height:1.8;max-width:680px;margin-bottom:32px}
.auto-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(260px,1fr));gap:20px;margin:48px 0}.auto-card{padding:36px 28px;border-radius:20px;border:1px solid var(--gray-100);background:var(--white);transition:all .5s var(--ease-out)}.auto-card:hover{border-color:var(--accent-light);transform:translateY(-4px);box-shadow:0 16px 40px rgba(0,0,0,.05)}.auto-card h3{font-family:var(--font-heading);font-size:1.1rem;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:8px}.auto-card p{font-size:.85rem;font-weight:300;color:var(--gray-600);line-height:1.6}.auto-card .label{font-size:.65rem;letter-spacing:.2em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--accent-dark);margin-bottom:12px;display:block}
.flow-diagram{background:var(--black);border-radius:24px;padding:48px 36px;margin:48px 0;color:var(--white);text-align:center}.flow-diagram h3{font-family:var(--font-heading);font-size:1.3rem;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:24px}.flow-steps{display:flex;justify-content:center;align-items:center;gap:12px;flex-wrap:wrap}.flow-step{padding:12px 20px;border-radius:12px;background:rgba(255,255,255,.06);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08);font-size:.82rem;color:rgba(255,255,255,.7)}.flow-arrow{color:var(--accent);font-size:1.2rem}
.page-cta{text-align:center;padding:100px 24px;background:linear-gradient(180deg,var(--gray-50),#f0ebe3,var(--gray-50))}.page-cta h2{max-width:600px;margin:0 auto 16px}.page-cta p{font-size:1rem;color:var(--gray-600);max-width:480px;margin:0 auto 32px;line-height:1.7;font-weight:300}
.btn-primary{font-family:var(--font-body);font-size:.88rem;font-weight:500;padding:16px 36px;background:var(--black);color:var(--white);border:none;border-radius:14px;cursor:pointer;text-decoration:none;display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;transition:all .4s var(--ease-out)}.btn-primary::after{content:'→';transition:transform .3s}.btn-primary:hover{transform:translateY(-2px);box-shadow:0 12px 32px rgba(166,139,94,.3);background:var(--accent-dark)}
.footer-mini{text-align:center;padding:40px 24px;border-top:1px solid var(--gray-100);font-size:.72rem;color:var(--gray-400)}.footer-mini a{color:var(--accent-dark);text-decoration:none}
.reveal{opacity:0;transform:translateY(40px);transition:opacity .9s var(--ease-out),transform .9s var(--ease-out)}.reveal.visible{opacity:1;transform:translateY(0)}
@media(max-width:700px){.nav{padding:0 20px}.nav-links{display:none}.flow-steps{flex-direction:column}.flow-arrow{transform:rotate(90deg)}}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<nav class="nav"><a href="/"><img src="/logo-transparent.png" alt="303" class="nav-logo"></a><ul class="nav-links"><li><a href="/">Inicio</a></li><li><a href="/#servicios">Servicios</a></li><li><a href="/auditoria.html">Auditoría</a></li></ul><a href="/#auditoria" class="nav-cta">Solicitar Auditoría</a></nav>
<div class="page-hero"><div class="tag">Servicio · Marketing & Automatización</div><h1>Marketing que trabaja<br>mientras tú duermes.</h1><p>Combinamos estrategia de contenido, ads pagos y automatización con IA para generar clientes de forma sistemática y escalable.</p></div>
<section><div class="inner"><div class="section-tag reveal">Automatización</div><h2 class="reveal">Sistemas que generan<br>clientes en automático.</h2><p class="text-block reveal">No hacemos marketing manual. Construimos sistemas automatizados que capturan, nutren y convierten leads mientras tú te enfocas en tu negocio.</p>
<div class="flow-diagram reveal"><h3>Flujo de automatización</h3><div class="flow-steps"><div class="flow-step">Lead entra por web/ads</div><span class="flow-arrow">→</span><div class="flow-step">CRM captura datos</div><span class="flow-arrow">→</span><div class="flow-step">Email automático</div><span class="flow-arrow">→</span><div class="flow-step">Seguimiento inteligente</div><span class="flow-arrow">→</span><div class="flow-step">Cierre de venta</div></div></div>
<div class="auto-grid">
<div class="auto-card reveal"><span class="label">Contenido</span><h3>Social Media Management</h3><p>Estrategia, diseño y publicación de contenido en Instagram, Facebook, LinkedIn. 12-20 posts/mes con copywriting profesional.</p></div>
<div class="auto-card reveal"><span class="label">Ads</span><h3>Paid Advertising</h3><p>Campañas en Meta Ads y Google Ads optimizadas para conversión. Segmentación precisa, A/B testing y reportes semanales.</p></div>
<div class="auto-card reveal"><span class="label">Email</span><h3>Email Marketing</h3><p>Welcome sequences, nurture flows, campañas mensuales. Automatización que convierte suscriptores en clientes.</p></div>
<div class="auto-card reveal"><span class="label">CRM</span><h3>CRM & Pipeline</h3><p>Configuración completa de Notion/HubSpot como CRM. Tracking de leads, scoring automático y seguimiento organizado.</p></div>
<div class="auto-card reveal"><span class="label">Automatización</span><h3>n8n & Make Workflows</h3><p>Flujos automatizados que conectan tu web, CRM, email y calendario. Un sistema que opera solo.</p></div>
<div class="auto-card reveal"><span class="label">Análisis</span><h3>Analytics & Reportes</h3><p>Dashboards en tiempo real, KPIs claros, recomendaciones accionables. Tomas decisiones con datos, no con intuición.</p></div>
</div></div></section>
<div class="page-cta"><div class="section-tag">¿Listo para automatizar?</div><h2>Deja de perseguir clientes.<br>Haz que te encuentren.</h2><p>Agenda tu auditoría y descubre cómo un sistema de marketing automatizado puede transformar tu negocio.</p><a href="/#auditoria" class="btn-primary">Solicitar Auditoría →</a></div>
<div class="footer-mini"><p>© 2026 303 Creative Studio® · <a href="/">Volver al inicio</a></p></div>
<script>const r=document.querySelectorAll('.reveal');const o=new IntersectionObserver(e=>{e.forEach(i=>{if(i.isIntersecting)i.target.classList.add('visible')})},{threshold:.1,rootMargin:'0px 0px -40px 0px'});r.forEach(el=>o.observe(el))</script>
</body></html>
